author: Swagata Dam
title: This Newlywed TV Couple Is Honeymooning In Switzerland
text:
A post shared by Sugandha Sood (@stylebysugandhasood) on Mar 4, 2017 at 9:03pm PST 
A while ago, Naagarjuna actress Pooja Banerjee tied the knot with her sportswoman beau, Sandeep Sejwal . Currently, the adorable couple is honeymooning in Switzerland. Here are some photos and videos of their romantic trip. A post shared by Pooja Banerjee ❤️🏊 (@poojabanerjeee) on Mar 6, 2017 at 4:48am PST A post shared by Sandeep (@sandeepsejwal) on Mar 7, 2017 at 8:40am PST A post shared by Pooja Banerjee ❤️🏊 (@poojabanerjeee) on Mar 6, 2017 at 8:15pm PST A post shared by Sandeep (@sandeepsejwal) on Mar 6, 2017 at 6:09am PST A post shared by Pooja Banerjee ❤️🏊 (@poojabanerjeee) on Mar 7, 2017 at 2:48am PST A post shared by Pooja Banerjee ❤️🏊 (@poojabanerjeee) on Mar 8, 2017 at 7:53am PST A post shared by Pooja Banerjee ❤️🏊 (@poojabanerjeee) on Mar 9, 2017 at 12:58am PST A post shared by Pooja Banerjee ❤️🏊 (@poojabanerjeee) on Mar 9, 2017 at 6:59am PST A post shared by Pooja Banerjee ❤️🏊 (@poojabanerjeee) on Mar 10, 2017 at 12:48am PST 
Here’s to the lovebirds! 0
